==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:50%\"\n|- bgcolor=\"#bebebe\"\n! width=\"10%\" | Year\n! width=\"30%\" | Car\n! width=\"10%\" | Points\n|-\n| rowspan=\"8\" style=\"text-align:center\" | '''2001'''\n|- style=\"background:#FCE44B\"\n| '''[[Alfa Romeo 147]]'''\n| '''238'''\n|- style=\"background:#D8D8D8\"\n| [[Ford Mondeo]]\n| 237\n|- style=\"background:#CEA621\"\n| [[Toyota Prius (XW10)|Toyota Prius]]\n| 229\n|- \n| [[Audi A2]]\n| 184\n|- \n| [[Mercedes-Benz C-Class (W203)|Mercedes-Benz C-Class]]\n| 164\n|-\n| [[Opel Corsa]]\n| 133\n|- \n| [[Volvo S60]]\n| 92\n|-\n| rowspan=\"8\" style=\"text-align:center\" | '''2002'''\n|- style=\"background:#FCE44B\"\n| '''[[Peugeot 307]]'''\n| '''286'''\n|- style=\"background:#D8D8D8\"\n| [[Renault Laguna]]\n| 244\n|- style=\"background:#CEA621\"\n| [[Fiat Stilo]]\n| 243\n|- \n| [[Mini Hatch|Mini One]]\n| 213\n|- \n| [[Honda Civic (seventh generation)|Honda Civic]]\n| 174\n|-\n| [[Citroen C5]]\n| 119\n|- \n| [[Jaguar X-Type]]\n| 86\n|-\n| rowspan=\"8\" style=\"text-align:center\" | '''2003'''\n|- style=\"background:#FCE44B\"\n| '''[[Renault M\u00e9gane]]'''\n| '''322'''\n|- style=\"background:#D8D8D8\"\n| [[Mazda 6]]\n| 302\n|- style=\"background:#CEA621\"\n| [[Citro\u00ebn C3]]\n| 214\n|- \n| [[Honda Fit|Honda Jazz]]\n| 167\n|- \n| [[Ford Fiesta]]\n| 161\n|-\n| [[Opel Vectra]]\n| 151\n|- \n| [[Mercedes-Benz E-Class (W211)|Mercedes-Benz E-Class]]\n| 133\n|-\n| rowspan=\"8\" style=\"text-align:center\" | '''2004'''\n|- style=\"background:#FCE44B\"\n| '''[[Fiat Panda#Second_generation_(2003%E2%80%932012)|Fiat Panda]]'''\n| '''281'''\n|- style=\"background:#D8D8D8\"\n| [[Mazda 3]]\n| 241\n|- style=\"background:#CEA621\"\n| [[Volkswagen Golf Mk5|Volkswagen Golf]]\n| 241\n|- \n| [[Toyota Avensis]]\n| 219\n|- \n| [[Opel Meriva]]\n| 213\n|-\n| [[BMW 5 Series (E60)|BMW 5 Series]]\n| 144\n|- \n| [[Nissan Micra]]\n| 111\n|-\n| rowspan=\"8\" style=\"text-align:center\" | '''2005'''\n|- style=\"background:#FCE44B\"\n| '''[[Toyota Priu