lkswagen Golf Mk6|Volkswagen Golf]]\n| 223 \n|- \n| [[Citroen C5#RD|Citroen C5]]\n| 198\n|- \n| [[Alfa Romeo MiTo]]\n| 148\n|-\n| [[\u0160koda Superb#B6|\u0160koda Superb]]\n| 144\n|- \n| [[Renault Megane#III|Renault Megane]]\n| 121\n|-\n| rowspan=\"8\" style=\"text-align:center\" | '''2010'''\n|- style=\"background:#FCE44B\"\n| '''[[Volkswagen Polo Mk5|Volkswagen Polo]]'''\n| '''347'''\n|- style=\"background:#D8D8D8\"\n| [[Toyota iQ]]\n| 337 \n|- style=\"background:#CEA621\"\n| [[Opel Astra#J|Opel Astra]]\n| 221 \n|- \n| [[\u0160koda Yeti]]\n| 158\n|- \n| [[Mercedes-Benz E-Class (W212)|Mercedes-Benz E-Class]]\n| 155\n|-\n| [[Peugeot 3008#First|Peugeot 3008]]\n| 144\n|- \n| [[Citroen C3 Picasso]]\n| 113\n|-\n| rowspan=\"8\" style=\"text-align:center\" | '''2011'''\n|- style=\"background:#FCE44B\"\n| '''[[Nissan Leaf]]'''\n| '''257'''\n|- style=\"background:#D8D8D8\"\n| [[Alfa Romeo Giulietta (2010)|Alfa Romeo Giulietta]]\n| 248 \n|- style=\"background:#CEA621\"\n| [[Opel Meriva#B|Opel Meriva]]\n| 244 \n|- \n| [[Ford C-Max#C344|Ford C-Max]]\n| 224\n|- \n| [[DS 3| Citroen DS3]]\n| 175\n|-\n| [[Volvo S60]]\n| 145\n|- \n| [[Dacia Duster]]\n| 132\n|-\n| rowspan=\"8\" style=\"text-align:center\" | '''2012'''\n|- style=\"background:#FCE44B\"\n| '''[[Chevrolet Volt]]/[[Opel Ampera]]'''\n| '''330'''\n|- style=\"background:#D8D8D8\"\n| [[Volkswagen up!]]\n| 281\n|- style=\"background:#CEA621\"\n| [[Ford Focus (third generation)|Ford Focus]]\n| 256 \n|- \n| [[Range Rover Evoque]]\n| 186\n|- \n| [[Fiat Panda]]\n| 156\n|-\n| [[DS 5|Citroen DS5]]\n| 144\n|- \n| [[Toyota Yaris#XP130|Toyota Yaris]]\n| 122\n|-\n| rowspan=\"8\" style=\"text-align:center\" | '''2013'''\n|- style=\"background:#FCE44B\"\n| '''[[Volkswagen Golf Mk7|Volkswagen Golf]]'''<ref name=\"Car of the Year twice\">{{cite web|title=Car of the Year twice - 1992 & 2013|url=http://www.volkswagen.co.uk/new/golf-vii/explore/reviews-and-awards|work=Car manufacturer|publisher=Volkswagen|accessdate=24 April 2013|archive-url