 (E60)|BMW 5 Series]]\n| 144\n|- \n| [[Nissan Micra]]\n| 111\n|-\n| rowspan=\"8\" style=\"text-align:center\" | '''2005'''\n|- style=\"background:#FCE44B\"\n| '''[[Toyota Prius (XW20)|Toyota Prius]]'''\n| '''406'''\n|- style=\"background:#D8D8D8\"\n| [[Citro\u00ebn C4]]\n| 267\n|- style=\"background:#CEA621\"\n| [[Ford Focus (second generation, Europe)|Ford Focus]]\n| 228\n|- \n|[[Opel Astra#H|Opel Astra]]\n| 180\n|- \n| [[Renault Modus]]\n| 151\n|-\n| [[Peugeot 407]]\n| 135\n|- \n| [[BMW 1 Series (E87)|BMW 1 Series]]\n| 83\n|-\n| rowspan=\"8\" style=\"text-align:center\" | '''2006'''\n|- style=\"background:#FCE44B\"\n| '''[[Renault Clio]]'''\n| '''256'''\n|- style=\"background:#D8D8D8\"\n| [[Volkswagen Passat (B6)|Volkswagen Passat]]\n| 251\n|- style=\"background:#CEA621\"\n| [[Alfa Romeo 159]]\n| 212\n|- \n| [[BMW 3 Series (E90)|BMW 3 Series]]\n| 203\n|- \n| [[Mazda Premacy#Second|Mazda 5]]\n| 198\n|-\n| [[Citroen C1]]\n| 187\n|- \n| [[Toyota Yaris#XP90|Toyota Yaris]]\n| 143\n|-\n| rowspan=\"8\" style=\"text-align:center\" | '''2007'''\n|- style=\"background:#FCE44B\"\n| '''[[Ford S-MAX|Ford S-Max]]'''\n| '''235'''\n|- style=\"background:#D8D8D8\"\n| [[Opel Corsa#D|Opel Corsa]]\n| 233\n|- style=\"background:#CEA621\"\n| [[Citro\u00ebn C4 Picasso]]\n| 222 \n|- \n| [[\u0160koda Roomster]]\n| 189\n|- \n| [[Honda Civic (eighth generation)|Honda Civic]]\n| 148\n|-\n| [[Peugeot 207]]\n| 144\n|- \n| [[Volvo C30]]\n| 141\n|-\n| rowspan=\"8\" style=\"text-align:center\" | '''2008'''\n|- style=\"background:#FCE44B\"\n| '''[[Fiat 500 (2007)|Fiat 500]]'''\n| '''385'''\n|- style=\"background:#D8D8D8\"\n| [[Mazda2]]\n| 325 \n|- style=\"background:#CEA621\"\n| [[Ford Mondeo]]\n| 202 \n|- \n| [[Kia Ceed#ED|Kia Ceed]]\n| 166\n|- \n| [[Nissan Qashqai#J10|Nissan Qashqai]]\n| 147\n|-\n| [[Mercedes-Benz C-Class (W204)|Mercedes-Benz C-Class]]\n| 128\n|- \n| [[Peugeot 308#T7|Peugeot 308]]\n| 91\n|-\n| rowspan=\"8\" style=\"text-align:center\" | '''2009'''\n|- style=\"background:#FCE44B\